@rule cache_keys
- Key shapes:
  - `${prefix}:id:${id}`
  - `${prefix}:list:${sha256Hex(stableStringify(filters))}`
- SWR: enable when ttlSec>0 and swrSec>0.
- Invalidate both id-based and list-based keys in afterCreate/afterUpdate/afterDelete.

@example
await this.cache.deleteKeysByPattern('articles:list:*');
await this.cache.delete(`articles:id:${id}`);
